CollectionWarnings.6776: This film is a 15 certificate, please bring valid photographic ID (e.g. passport, ID with the PASS symbol, YOTI card) we will be doing checks.
CollectionWarnings.6781: This screening is exclusively for pre-school children and their parents or carers. Unaccompanied adults and children will not be admitted
CollectionWarnings.6982: This film is an 18 certificate. Please bring valid photographic ID (e.g. passport or drivers license) with you as our team will be doing checks.
CollectionWarnings.7037: This screening has open captions/subtitles at the bottom of the screen to assist those who are hard of hearing.
CollectionWarnings.7038: This screening is exclusively for parents and carers with babies under one year old. Older children will not be admitted.
CollectionWarnings.7039: Open to all, but specially designed to help people with sensory sensitivity enjoy the cinema. This screening will have no ads or trailers
CollectionWarnings.7319: Please be aware you will need to either bring or buy a pair of 3D glasses to enjoy this screening. These are available at the cinema for £1.50.
